                        <interp inst="t18700711-543-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">He was further charged with having been convicted of a like offence at this Court, in March,</hi> 1869, <hi rend="italic">to which he</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
PLEADED GUILTY</hi>**—<hi rend="italic">
